{"id": 1247, "genre": 1000, "title": "你期待在地铁上看到哪些更活泼的信息？", "description": "地铁，一个当代信息公告栏。为何我每次却只在看“小心缝隙”及其英文。（题图来自：Olivier Bonhomme）", "record_count": 6060, "comment_count": 30, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160927153212GQsY21qCytS8rFVJ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-09-28T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 1138, "title": "你期待在地铁上看到哪些更活泼的信息？", "content": "你期待在地铁上看到哪些更活泼的信息？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 119783, "content": "每个站点配个二维码，扫一扫出现当站好玩的地方", "image": "img/option/option/20160927163034vFChoxNQXE3jB46D.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 119785, "content": "车里有不同的屏幕可以看，从电视剧到体育赛事资讯", "image": "img/option/option/20160927163048pUxr6egD7O3HuoFl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 119797, "content": "车内显示切实有用的信息，比如NBA比分，本地餐馆优惠", "image": "img/option/option/20160927163429AkTa9uqD6IC8HNYj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 119792, "content": "站台有切实有用的信息，比如本月周边房价", "image": "img/option/option/20160927163403Xn0xFtYWMQK3uZvj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 119793, "content": "到站显示本站的公用设备，比如便利店，厕所，麦当劳", "image": "img/option/option/20160927163415t7TnK4EyB5N9YhSk.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 119802, "content": "站外有效信息显示，比如提示我出站后有几辆公共自行车可以用", "image": "img/option/option/20160929090642djQVD9Nz7gTluoAa.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 119791, "content": "想要多一些趣味性的合作款列车，比如地铁样板间", "image": "img/option/option/201609271631143dCO8vAFqfbtnco1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}